<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.4.9">
<l>kaṇṇaṉai māyaṉ ṟaṉṉaik kaṭalkaṭain tamutaṅ koṇṭa</l>
<l>vaṇṇalai yaccu taṉṉai yaṉantaṉai yaṉantaṉ ṟaṉmē</l>
<l>ṉaṇṇinaṉ kuṟaikiṉ ṟāṉai ñālamuṇ ṭumiḻnta mālai</l>
<l>yeṇṇumā ṟaṟiya māṭṭēṉ yāvaiyum yavarun tāṉē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Kṛṣṇa, the trickster, the majesty who churned the ocean [and] took</l>
<l>the ambrosia, the unshakable one, the unending one, the one who rests</l>
<l>well, staying on Ananta, Māl who swallowed [and] spir out the world,</l>
<l>I don’t know a way to account for him. He is everthing and everyone.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
